            <h3>Pretoria</h3>
            <p>Loftus Versfeld Stadium, Kirkness Street<br>Pretoria, 0002<br>+27 12 345 6789</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- FAQ Section -->
<section class="upcoming-events">
    <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
    <p>Find answers to commonly asked questions about our organization</p>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="event-col">
            <h3>How can I register for events?</h3>
            <p>Event registration can be done through our website by creating an account and navigating to the specific event page. You can also register in person at any of our regional offices.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="event-col">
            <h3>How can I become a member?</h3>
            <p>Membership applications can be submitted online through our website or in person at our offices. Different membership categories are available for athletes, coaches, officials, and supporters.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="event-col">
            <h3>Do you offer sponsorship opportunities?</h3>
            <p>Yes, we offer various sponsorship packages for businesses and organizations interested in supporting South African sports. Please contact our partnerships team at partnerships@sasports.org.za for more information.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

